unidue.ub.statistics.analysis

Class DocumentAnalysis

  • java.lang.Object
    • unidue.ub.statistics.analysis.DocumentAnalysis
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<DocumentAnalysis>

    @Entity
public class DocumentAnalysis
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<DocumentAnalysis>
    Plain old java object holding an analysis of one year and one document. The fields can be persisted.
    Version:
    1
    Author:
    Eike Spielberg

      Constructors

      DocumentAnalysis()
      Builds a new instance of a DocumentAnalysis-object, setting the individual counters to 0 and the text fields to an empty string.
